data.description: Inviting Smart Home with Solar!  3 bedroom plus Office/Den has tile flooring throughout the living area. Open concept with high ceiling and recessed lighting has kitchen, dining area and great room opening to one another. The kitchen features granite counter tops, breakfast bar, tall cabinets, walk in pantry and tiled backsplash. The great room has boxed ceiling with crown and has access to covered porch. The master bedroom has boxed ceiling, bath with granite top double vanity, tiled shower and spacious walk-in closet with built ins. The guest bedrooms share a bath with granite top vanity. Upgraded features include attic stairs, rain gutters, irrigation system, tiled backsplash, landscaping, Solar, Fenced back yard, organized system in Master bedroom closet, cabinets in laundry and Smart Home Security System that seller monitors.  Community area with play equipment. This upgraded home is move in ready. If you are looking for move in ready, comfort and style this home is for you!
